comments.body: I've seen European Columbine growing wild, and it comes in a variety of colours, but I don't think it ever looks like this.
Thanks Reuven, I knew it was the only native Columbine locally, but could not remember if Western or other invasive species were present.
The only native columbine in Southern Ontario
